---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Industries We Serve | Hashir Khan | AI Automation by Vertical" description="Industry-specific AI automation for real estate, healthcare, legal, restaurants, ecommerce, education, construction, marketing agencies, travel, and immigration." canonical="https://hashir.ai/industries">
	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>AI automation for your industry<span class="period">.</span></h1>
			<p>Every industry has different workflows, compliance needs, and pain points. We tailor every agent to fit yours.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section-padding">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="industries-list">
				<!-- Real Estate -->
				<article id="real-estate" class="industry-detail reveal-on-scroll">
					<div class="industry-detail-header">
						<span class="card-meta-tag mono">INDUSTRY_01 // REAL_ESTATE</span>
						<h2>Real Estate</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Agents spend hours qualifying property inquiries, scheduling viewings, and following up with cold leads. Inquiries come through WhatsApp, Instagram, email, and phone — all disconnected. Hot leads go cold because response time is measured in hours, not seconds.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>AI agent that qualifies buyer/renter intent on WhatsApp before the agent wakes up</li>
								<li>Automated property listing suggestions based on budget, location, and preferences</li>
								<li>Self-serve viewing scheduling with calendar sync for each agent or property</li>
								<li>Automated follow-up sequences for unsold inquiries (7-day, 30-day, 90-day)</li>
								<li>Lead scoring by budget range, timeline urgency, and property type interest</li>
								<li>Integration with property management systems (custom API or MLS feeds)</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-cta-row">
							<a href="https://calendly.com/hashirkhan" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Book a discovery call</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

				<!-- Healthcare -->
				<article id="healthcare" class="industry-detail reveal-on-scroll" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-hairline);padding-top:64px;margin-top:48px;">
					<div class="industry-detail-header">
						<span class="card-meta-tag mono">INDUSTRY_02 // HEALTHCARE</span>
						<h2>Healthcare</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Clinics lose 30%+ of inbound calls to voicemail. Staff spends 20+ hours/week on appointment scheduling. No-show rates hit 35% because reminder systems are manual. Patient intake forms are still paper-based in many practices.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>WhatsApp/voice AI agent for 24/7 appointment booking and rescheduling</li>
								<li>Automated patient intake form collection via chat before the visit</li>
								<li>Multi-provider schedule management with conflict resolution</li>
								<li>Automated reminder sequences (24h, 2h, 15min) via SMS and WhatsApp</li>
								<li>HIPAA-aware data handling with encryption and access controls</li>
								<li>Post-visit follow-up and feedback collection automation</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-cta-row">
							<a href="https://calendly.com/hashirkhan" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Book a discovery call</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

				<!-- Immigration -->
				<article id="immigration" class="industry-detail reveal-on-scroll" style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-hairline);padding-top:64px;margin-top:48px;">
					<div class="industry-detail-header">
						<span class="card-meta-tag mono">INDUSTRY_03 // IMMIGRATION</span>
						<h2>Immigration Consulting</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Immigration consultants answer the same eligibility questions dozens of times daily. Document collection is manual and error-prone. Clients struggle to understand visa timelines, and follow-up communication across multiple time zones is chaotic.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>AI eligibility triage — answers visa category questions based on current immigration rules</li>
								<li>Automated document request and collection workflows via secure chat</li>
								<li>Case status tracking with proactive client updates via WhatsApp</li>
								<li>Consultation booking synced with consultant calendar and time zones</li>
								<li>Multi-language support for international client communication</li>
								<li>CRM integration for case pipeline management</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-cta-row">
							<a href="https://calendly.com/hashirkhan" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Book a discovery call</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

