						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Firms waste billable hours on client intake screening, consultation scheduling, and answering basic case eligibility questions. Document preparation is repetitive. Client communication across multiple practices is inconsistent.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>AI client intake agent that screens case type, conflicts, and urgency before booking</li>
								<li>Automated consultation scheduling with practice-area routing</li>
								<li>Document template automation for engagement letters, intake forms, disclosures</li>
								<li>Secure client portal with status updates and document request workflows</li>
								<li>Practice management software integration (Clio, MyCase, or custom)</li>
								<li>Confidentiality-compliant architecture with data isolation per client</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-cta-row">
							<a href="https://calendly.com/hashirkhan" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Book a discovery call</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>

