					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Restaurants get flooded with reservation calls during peak hours — and miss walk-in customers because staff is on the phone. Waitlist management is manual. No-show rates hurt revenue. Promotional outreach is non-existent because there's no capacity.</p>
