					<div class="industry-detail-header">
						<span class="card-meta-tag mono">INDUSTRY_07 // EDUCATION</span>
						<h2>Education & Training</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Schools and training centers handle hundreds of enrollment inquiries per week — most asking the same questions about fees, schedules, and admission requirements. Application processing is manual and slow. Parent communication is inconsistent.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
