					</div>
					<div class="industry-detail-body">
						<div class="industry-pain">
							<h3>Common pain points</h3>
							<p>Agencies manage multiple client accounts, each with different reporting cadences, ad platforms, and communication channels. Reporting is manual. Lead follow-up for agency's own services is ad-hoc. Client onboarding involves repetitive data collection.</p>
