							<p>500+ daily customer inquiries about orders, returns, and sizing overwhelm support teams. Abandoned cart recovery is manual or non-existent. Inventory queries and order tracking consume staff time. Post-purchase follow-up is inconsistent.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="industry-fit">
							<h3>How we help</h3>
