			<div class="preview-cta" style="margin-top:64px;padding-top:48px;border-top:1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
				<h2 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Don't see your industry<span class="period">?</span></h2>
				<p style="color:var(--color-body);margin-bottom:24px;max-width:500px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">We've built for 12+ industries. If you have a specific workflow in mind, we'd love to discuss it.</p>
